Vendored native source
----------------------

third_party/thorvg-sys/ vendors a patched fork of the thorvg-sys FFI
crate, which bundles the ThorVG C++ library used by the image viewer.
These components are compiled from source and statically linked into the
flowmux binary; their upstream license texts are retained in-tree:

    ThorVG            MIT           third_party/thorvg-sys/thorvg/LICENSE
    ThorVG jpg loader MIT           third_party/thorvg-sys/thorvg/src/loaders/jpg/
    WebP (libwebp)    BSD-3-Clause  third_party/thorvg-sys/thorvg/src/loaders/webp/LICENSE
                      + patent grant  (Copyright 2012 Google Inc.)
